600000 people failed to exchange their driver's license
600000 motorists missed the deadline to exchange their old driver's license, the validity of which expires at the end of the year.
Today is the last day where you can apply for the exchange so that the authorities manage to issue a new driver's license by the end of the year.
However, the ministry does not fear that after New Year, hundreds of thousands of drivers will take to the roads without a valid driving authorization.
According to the authorities, mainly those who do not want to drive have mostly exchanged their driver's license.
